      SimpleResult<com.radiotelescope.security.UserSession,com.google.common.collect.Multimap> execute()
      Execute method that will grab the SecurityContextHolder authentication token and, if it is not null, will determine if the user is an admin, and if so, return a class UserSession object. Otherwise, it will return an error.
